cast.original_title: All Quiet on the Western Front
cast.overview: When a group of idealistic young men join the German Army during the Great War, they are assigned to the Western Front, where their patriotism is destroyed by the harsh realities of combat.
cast.title: All Quiet on the Western Front

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Joan Marsh (born Nancy Ann Rosher, July 10, 1913 – August 10, 2000) was an American child actress in silent films between 1915 and 1921. Later, during the sound era, she resumed her acting career and performed in a variety of films during the 1930s and 1940s.
details.name: Joan Marsh
